Paper: hep-th/0107107

Date: 2001-07-12

Title: Geometric Phase in Quaternionic Quantum Mechanics

Authors: M. D. Maia and V. B. Bezerra

Comments: Latex. 14 pages, no figures. Updates most of hep-th/9904067, to

appear in the International Journal of Theoretical PhysicsJournal-ref: Int.J.Theor.Phys. 40 (2001) 1283-1294

Quaternion quantum mechanics is examined at the level of unbroken SU(2) gaugesymmetry. A general quaternionic phase expression is derived from formalproperties of the quaternion algebra.